k="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/12-steps-4-zero-clicks-how-the-u-s-hacked-the-iphone-to-spy-on-russia/0000018c-c0cd-d3e0-abac-d8ed05e00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的医疗报告显示身体状况良好，没有心脏异常</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-medical-report-shows-good-condition-no-cardiac-anomalies/0000018c-c08f-d3e0-abac-d8afcdeb0000</link><description>报告发布三天前，一名平民要求以色列总检察长公开内塔尼亚胡的健康状况，认为隐瞒这一情况会使允许宣布总理不适合任职的《基本法》失效。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 18:15:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-medical-report-shows-good-condition-no-cardiac-anomalies/0000018c-c08f-d3e0-abac-d8afcdeb0000</guid></item><item><title>比比和拜登，兄弟情谊的对立面：《国土报》关于 2023 年美以关系的重要报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article-timeline/.premium/bibi-and-biden-the-anti-bromance-key-haaretz-stories-on-u-s-israel-relations-in-2023/0000018c-c021-d4e1-ad8f-fcb1a1920000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 17:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article-timeline/.premium/bibi-and-biden-the-anti-bromance-key-haaretz-stories-on-u-s-israel-relations-in-2023/0000018c-c021-d4e1-ad8f-fcb1a1920000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年是以色列有史以来最糟糕的一年。它以一些希望的痕迹结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-israels-worst-year-ever-it-ends-with-a-few-traces-of-hope/0000018c-c043-d4e1-ad8f-fcf349300000</link><description>这是以色列最命运的一年，内忧外患的矛盾暴露和加剧了国家的核心矛盾。人们第一次对以色列能否继续遏制这些矛盾产生了重大疑问——但一切还没有结束</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 16:28:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-israels-worst-year-ever-it-ends-with-a-few-traces-of-hope/0000018c-c043-d4e1-ad8f-fcf349300000</guid></item><item><title>真主党副领袖表示以色列必须停止加沙战争才能结束黎巴嫩的战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-deputy-chief-says-israel-must-stop-gaza-war-for-combat-in-lebanon-to-end/0000018c-c066-d6c4-ab8d-e1f600220000</link><description>据报道，美国调解员阿莫斯·霍赫斯坦将很快访问黎巴嫩，试图安排停火。以色列总理内塔尼亚胡表示，“如果我们不能通过外交实现我们的目标，我们将通过军事手段实现”</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 15:56:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-deputy-chief-says-israel-must-stop-gaza-war-for-combat-in-lebanon-to-end/0000018c-c066-d6c4-ab8d-e1f600220000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列精神卫生系统面临崩溃，数十名精神科医生前往英国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-system-in-israel-collapses-psychiatrists-are-leaving-for-britain/0000018c-c026-d3e0-abac-d8af89aa0000</link><description>消息人士将人才外流归因于工作量不断增加，并认为情况只会恶化，因为卫生部修复该系统的计划仍在等待财政部的资金批准</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 15:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-system-in-israel-collapses-psychiatrists-are-leaving-for-britain/0000018c-c026-d3e0-abac-d8af89aa0000</guid></item><item><title>一名加沙男孩梦想打破互联网。他做到了——在以色列炸弹炸死他之后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/a-gaza-boy-dreamed-of-breaking-the-internet-he-did-after-an-israeli-bomb-killed-him/0000018c-bfcb-d4e1-ad8f-bffbc01b0000</link><description>13 岁的 Awni Eldous 经营着一个 YouTube 频道，梦想成为一名有影响力的人。他的故事在世界各地引起共鸣，代表了加沙儿童在战争中的悲剧</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 14:48:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/a-gaza-boy-dreamed-of-breaking-the-internet-he-did-after-an-israeli-bomb-killed-him/0000018c-bfcb-d4e1-ad8f-bffbc01b0000</guid></item><item><title>“100-20万，而不是200万”：以色列财政部长设想加沙人口减少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/100-200-000-not-two-million-israels-finance-minister-envisions-depopulated-gaza/0000018c-bfe8-d6c4-ab8d-fffc0b910000</link><description>以色列极右翼财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇与越来越多的高级立法者一起表示支持大规模转移加沙平民，以解决以色列战后安全问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 14:46:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/100-200-000-not-two-million-israels-finance-minister-envisions-depopulated-gaza/0000018c-bfe8-d6c4-ab8d-fffc0b910000</guid></item><item><title>美国对以色列的支持就没有红线吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/are-there-no-red-lines-to-u-s-support-for-israel/0000018c-bf3a-d45c-a98e-bf7ea92b0000</link><description>10月7日是一起令人发指的罪行。但是，有多少加沙人必须死去，有多少以色列部长必须推动种族清洗，内塔尼​​亚胡必须否认多少失败——美国才能重新考虑其对以色列政府发动的邪恶战争的不道德、无条件的支持？</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/are-there-no-red-lines-to-u-s-support-for-israel/0000018c-bf3a-d45c-a98e-bf7ea92b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙战争，以色列内阁投票决定将地方选举推迟至2月底</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-votes-to-delay-local-elections-until-late-february-due-to-gaza-war/0000018c-bffd-d6c4-ab8d-fffd56ab0000</link><description>以色列国防军数据显示，数百名候选人在预备役中服役，无法被释放，选举第二次推迟，但代表预备役候选人的律师表示，推迟选举“具有讽刺意味的是，这增加了对手的优势”</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:39:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-votes-to-delay-local-elections-until-late-february-due-to-gaza-war/0000018c-bffd-d6c4-ab8d-fffd56ab0000</guid></item><item><title>赛车无人机军备竞赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/the-racing-drones-arms-race/0000018c-bf91-d6c4-ab8d-ffb5243a0000</link><description>FPV 无人机凭借 150 公里/小时的疯狂机动性，已成为乌克兰战场上精确、致命的制导武器。对他们的防御是有限的。他们很快就会出现在我们的舞台上吗？以色列准备好了吗？</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">ht